Description:
    Create all it's necessary for an administration area for Fator P's Applications

Example:
    rails generate admin_layout

    This will create:
        app/controllers/admin/admin_controller.rb
        config/credentials/yml
        app/views/layouts/admin.html.haml
        app/stylesheets/admin.sass
        public/javascripts/admin.js
        mkdir app/views/admin

